quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,56,"Nuzen ik id kan, i ubecceĂŽ d uneddeĂŽ"
  25,57,"Ini: \"ur awen ssutre$, $ef waya, kra n teqdiĂąt. Ssutre$ kan, i win ib$an, ad ia$ abrid $eĂŽ Mass is"
  25,58,Ppkel $ef Umuddir ur Nepmeppat. SbuccaĂą iT s ccekĂŽan. Iqadd i tussna ibekkaven n imdanen iS
  25,59,"I Ixelqen tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan. Sinna, AĂȘnin IĂąannec af usgeld. Steqsi w iT issnen"
  25,60,"Ma pwanecden: \"knut i UĂȘnin\"! A d rren: \"d acu T UĂȘnin? Day a neknu i w ara $ d tamĂŽev\"? D a$unfu i sen irna"
  25,61,"Ad IĂŽqu Win Irran itran deg igenni. Irna degs, lefnaĂŽ, akked waggur bu tziri"
  25,62,"D Neppa i Irran iv akked wass mestebĂąan, i win ib$an ad ismekti, ne$ ib$an ad isnemmer"
  25,63,"Ixdimen n UĂȘnin, i ileĂȘĂȘun di tmurt di lehna, ma numren ten at war tussna, qqaĂŽen: \"tifrat"
  25,64,"I ippaĂąwazen i Mass nnsen, knan ne$ bedden"
  25,65,"I iqqaĂŽen: \"a Mass nne$! VeĂŽĂŽef segne$ aĂąaqeb n Loahennama. Ih, aĂąaqeb is ipwaĂȘeppem"
  25,66,"Neppat, s tidep, d tadirant, i tnezdu$t akked i$imi"
  25,67,"Wid, ma seĂŽĂŽfen, ur veggiĂąen, ur pcuĂȘĂȘun: igi iwulmen atan garasen"
